Method behavioural specifications:
- The integer matrix parameter `mat` must not be null.
- The integer matrix parameter `mat` must have at least one cell with the value `0`.
- The integer matrix result has the same dimensions as the integer matrix parameter `mat`.
- Each cell in the integer matrix result represents the distance to the nearest `0` cell in the integer matrix parameter `mat`.
- The distance between two adjacent cells in the integer matrix result is `1`.